{
  "stem": "8753.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they weren't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, very seldom did we see Germans in town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They just came for-- for a reason, if they had to.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- then another time they-- like, we were suppose-- we were taxed so heavily that if we gave all the wheat away, we would have no wheat for our own use.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So my father gave a certain amount of wheat to the Germans, and then he felt-- you know, he will explain them that we need it for our family.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they came to-- to collect, you know, the-- the wheat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And our-- my mother used to be friendly with the mayor of the town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She used to cook-- if the mayor invited some officials, so he used to come to my mother to ask to cook the dinner for them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So she was friendly with him, so when-- during war, they used to tip us off if the Germans were coming.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when they tipped us off at the time that the Germans were coming to see that we didn't pay-- give the wheat to the Germans, my father and mother and brother ran away to the woods to hide.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we-- the girls, the three girls-- were left on the farm.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father told us, you have to tell.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And what we were doing, we were working in the barn shredding the wheat so when they come, they should see that we are working and so forth.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father explained it to us what we should say, that we need the wheat for ourselves and we gave as much as we could.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, they arrested us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took us in to jail.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were in Brody jail for a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not in Czernica.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Brody.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
